Uses of Package
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2

Packages that use io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2 
Package Description
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2
This package and its subpackages together comprise a Java implementation of the MOSDEX Reference Architecture (RefArc).
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.dataframe
This package represents alternative implementations of the Dataframe interface.
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.json
This package provides classes for reading and writing MOSDEX JSON objects to/from the MOSDEX object model.
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.modeling
This package includes classes and interfaces that support creation of solver-specific modeling objects, such as variables, constraints, etc.
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.objectModel
This package includes Java classes representing MOSDEX objects.
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.span
This package provides classes and interfaces that support streaming data from MOSDEX to a solver.

    DisplayWindow

    This class provides a fully configured optimization application using MOSDEX.

    Builder for MsdxContainer.
    MsdxFunctionCall
    This family of classes represent calls to a solver function for use in a MOSDEX Table schema.

    Provides a standard source for reading a MOSDEX JSON File.
    MsdxOutputDestination
    Provides a standard destination for writing a MOSDEX JSON File.
